other_tests.findings: Markedly degraded study by motion artifact; Mild bronchial impaction in the left lower lobe; Hepatic steatosis with 24% fat fraction; 4 mm calculus in distal CBD with 13 mm proximal bile duct dilatation; Smaller calculi in mid to distal CBD; No features of cholecystitis; Mild intrahepatic bile duct dilatation; Normal pancreatic parenchyma and pancreatic duct; No bowel obstruction.
